actionConfiguration.body: select tp.project_name ,tp.project_product ,tp.project_group ,tp.remarks,tpr .create_time ,tp.create_by  from t_project tp left join t_project_reord tpr on tp.id = tpr.project_id  where YEARWEEK(DATE_FORMAT(tpr .create_time ,'%Y-%m-%d')) = YEARWEEK({{DatePicker1.formattedDate}})-1 and  tp.status = 5  and tpr.status_type  = '已完成'  group by tp.id
